like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:35:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"787de40d2ae1507fa75d99ebbcac527d8c94e819","tid":1813842,"uid":24814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f7bfeafcd6351e8023e7ad05bf8ed996bfb4bad","tid":1813842,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:24:06.000Z","msg":"之前上水同九龍灣和你shop<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大量和理非手足無端白事被狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有見及此，想建議大家搞個防疫版和你shop<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>和你clean</strong></span></span><br />\n核心成員裝備&mdash;&mdash;董太裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1400000/1403659/biln20030413009_630_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1400000%2F1403659%2Fbiln20030413009_630_1024.jpg&h=a61c3c2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/sars15/files/timelinephoto/169/photo/1520873250-0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fsars15%2Ffiles%2Ftimelinephoto%2F169%2Fphoto%2F1520873250-0.jpg&h=3abe0ada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔係叫你真係著到成個董太咁，自己上去Amazon搵hazmat suit<br />\n買滿$49美元免運，順便同d口罩運返嚟香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本款有白色，另外仲有黃金戰衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/61maVIQ801L._UX342_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F61maVIQ801L._UX342_.jpg&h=5702178b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加埋個防毒面罩就可以開工喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n清潔工具：<br />\n1:99稀釋家用漂白水（未稀釋可能會俾狗咬，請自行斟酌）<br />\n毛巾同噴壺<br />\n漂白水使用方法可以參考政府網頁<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/info/sars/tc/useofbleach.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fsars%2Ftc%2Fuseofbleach.htm&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=e346b229\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/info/sars/tc/useofbleach.htm</a><br />\n路人所需裝備：平就外科口罩或貴少少N95(1860/1860S/1870/1870S)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行動方針：<br />\n去商場／藍店外幫手清潔，噴下抹下咁，視乎人流加減頻率，最基本每半小時一次<br />\n少人去咪唔使清潔得咁密囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n扶手／門柄／Lift掣要加緊清潔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有保安問你或者被截查，就同佢地講你係幫世衛做防疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為世界衛生站在最前線犯法呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾人趕就去出入口做清潔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果鄉黑曱甴王又玩濫捕而俾傳媒影到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n報紙條題就會係　香港警察打壓志願防疫工作者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個佛系仆街政府連武漢旅客自發分流都搞得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就知佢地根本冇心冇魄力去做好防疫工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地唔搞就由我地市民自己搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦想係度點名屌鳩陳肇始條仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果香港有確診個案，一定要困埋佢入隔離病房<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要佢用護士身份親手照顧支那肺炎病人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死咗最多幫佢立個像，紙紮果隻燒翻俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:35:35.000Z","msg":"清潔香港大行動 宣傳上話唔裝修齋清潔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫埋和理非同藍絲去做 <img src=\"/